HEADWORD: Atony
<hw>At"o*ny</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ slackness;
<grk>'a</grk> priv. + <?/ tone, strength, <?/ to stretch: cf. F.
<ets>atonie</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Want of tone; weakness
